Great coffee, consistent care, the usual selection of favs. My latest crave: Classic Bantam Bagels as seen on Shark Tank.  (Yes, its only coffee BUT maybe you haven't been to Eugene OR where, sadly, the homeless population is overwhelming. Rightly, these citizens will do anything to secure the bathroom code for morning clean up [guilty of giving code out-mad rush ensues-grab ur coffee & run]. Managers are managing! BUT, in Asheville NC, the City put up a port-a-potty outside Starbucks w sink & mirror which is what I call "municipalities accepting responsibility for all their citizens")  So, hats off to Bethesda hard-working staff for always having a smile & making my morning coffee a great experience as "committed masters of their trade."
